    "body": "Since colours are handled the same way for both fish and nushell, I assume that this is a bug in nushell.\n\nEdit: IIRC fish prints a colour reset at the end of the prompt, nushell may require this too. Does setting `$env.STARSHIP_SHELL` to `fish` fix the issue in nushell?",
