    "created_at": "2025-07-28T21:30:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-07-28T21:30:05Z",
    "body": "```toml\nformat = \"\"\"\n${custom.fix}\\\n\n..other fields....\n\"\"\"\n\n[custom.fix]\nformat = \"[\\b](bold)\"\nwhen = true\n\n```\n\nI have been able to achieve a fix whilst not displaying any visible characters by using `\\b` which is a backspace escape character.\n\nAll following modules now correctly display their (lack of) styling.\n\nNote: this is still a workaround and not a fix to the issue.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
    "reactions": {
