    "created_at": "2026-01-25T01:37:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-01-25T01:37:16Z",
    "body": "For anyone else on NixOS, it seems that (ab)using `builtins.fromJSON` is necessary to implement @egirlcatnip’s workaround:\n```nix\ncustom.fix = {\n  format = \"[${builtins.fromJSON ''\"\\b\"''}](bold)\";\n  when = true;\n};\n```",
